name: AgentTank
description: Your Own Web3 Superhero. A desktop crypto copilot that sees what you see, thinks how you think, and acts at the speed of conversation. From market research to token swaps, portfolio monitoring to computer automation - all through natural dialogue. Tank brings AI-powered collaboration while taking independent action on your behalf, becoming an indispensable part of your crypto daily routine. Experience the future of Web3, where advanced AI meets seamless execution.
